metadata.name: NAG-I Passion Fruit
metadata.description:
This gown is part of our first Collection “Noir Avant-Garde” by M.O.S

This collection has five clothes, 3 gowns and 2 suits, each one with nine unique color variations. Anyone who win the auction over 5 ethereum get the 3D item + design pattern to reproduce it in real life one time only. In case you want to reproduce it in mass scale (commercial use) please contact us here: https://www.linkedin.com/company/mos-digital-fashion
 
My Other Skin aka M.O.S is a Digital Fashion Brand which create 3DGarments ready to wear by your virtual avatars. Our mission bring utility and uniqueness to the NFT scene.  

P.S. The 3D file only includes digital garments.  Not our in-house model who appears in this video.  

We also provide service to create and personalize your avatars, please contact us: https://www.linkedin.com/company/mos-digital-fashion

---------
This NFT is using the track HIGH by Snoop Dogg. Because we are holding his NFT which grants that.
